Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me all about Nana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear about your feelings for her, and once I sort out me feelings about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met her in my second year of middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and she accidentally died during the summer of my third year. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what more can you determine from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the condition of him telling you about Nana-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that was just a trigger for you to forgive him...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.78,0:00:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try becoming a little more honest with your feelings?
