Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:29.86,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:35.82,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:41.95,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:47.92,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:55.30,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:02:00.01,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:05.93,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:14.82,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:19.74,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:26.87,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:33.63,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:29.86,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:35.82,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:41.95,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:47.92,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:55.30,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:02:00.01,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:05.93,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:14.82,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:19.74,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:26.87,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:33.63,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
