Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:52.27,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Yano to tell me about Nana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.98,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if I hear everything from Yano's lips..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:03:00.74,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H6B6D66&\fscx166.25\fscy172.5\pos(222,253)\frz5.746\frx10\fry4}Takahashi, next time\N I'll properly talk about\N Nana-san. So please\N meet with me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, next time I'll properly talk about Nana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please meet with me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all the bad feelings I have will fade away...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I might be able to really trust him this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, shoot! This isn't even a date...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll feel that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I might be able to make up with him and start over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I had to find the movie tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you? This isn't a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But these tickets expire today, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don't want to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They expire today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be such a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:28.33,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\b1\fscx205\fscy182.5\pos(601,154)\c&H545EFF&}Really\N Cheap
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.58,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\b1\fscx205\fscy182.5\pos(601,154)\c&H545EFF&}Really\N Cheap
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this just the same pattern as before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't watch a movie without getting some popcorn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salted butter popcorn. please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.94,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Caramel-flavored popcorn, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There's no way caramel ever goes with popcorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? Salted butter popcorn is so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want caramel, why don't you just get some candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caramel candy and popcorn are completely different!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly my point! If they're so different, why do you have to combine them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes good! You're the one who isn't making any sense, Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just get the salted butter popcorn, Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get my own caramel-flavored...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good... two like that, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What? I can pay for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! This isn't a date, so I don't think it's right for you to pay for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just split the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.65,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx187.5\fscy215\pos(320,-2)\c&H9816A9&}Sign: Devastation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you back! I'll definitely pay you back tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's like no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:06:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With it like this, everything's gonna go the way Yano wants it to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is pretty amazing. Besides the two of us, there's only three other couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it amaz... ing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to let you know, I'm giving up on you if you don't talk about her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I find it hard to believe you plan on talking seriously today, the way things are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano instinctively has a habit of avoiding Nana-san whenever the topic comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name was Yamamoto Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her birthday was July 29th. Her blood type was B.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for her family...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she had a mother, father, and a little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She loved going out to sing karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hated doing schoolwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her favourite color was pink. Her room was covered in hot pink everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had a silly personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd laugh a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd laugh at anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd even laugh at things that weren't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went out with ton of guys. By the way, I was the 7th.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm, that's not really what I wanted to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want a profile. I wanted more of, umm... you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, Yano's feelings for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... was there anything that really left an impression on you after going out with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that left an impression?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how an udon noodle once came out of her nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An udon noodle came out of her nose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were eating udon, and she started laughing really hard about something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really freaked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you she was silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the movie's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano keeps giving me the slip...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This movie's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just like before... his left hand's in the exact same position...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he leaving half of the armrest for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... why won't he hold my hand like he did before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you beat the boss yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just beat it today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted her to come back to life, didn't you? Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I hate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the woman I loved so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll forgive you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please... I want you to come back to me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Nana-san was saved in that accident... If she got out of it alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a really mean question...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to consider something like that in a normal sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd keep going out with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually... that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted her to come back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got caught up in this atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that how you really feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't answer any of the things I'm trying to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am answering you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep running away from my questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not running!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want from me?! What do I have to say so you'll understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm asking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something really big in Yano's heart, like a blockade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to consider something like that in a normal sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd keep going out with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And every time I try to get around it, he gets so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:11:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more he acts like he doesn't see it... the more I can feel it become even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That existence of the person who was Nana-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand Yano's feelings anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost all my confidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no meaning left in any of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's like getting a game over before you can beat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't supposed to be like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I just misunderstood things...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...thinking that I might've been able to get Yano to do something about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizu-chin's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Taka-chan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We Were There TOO!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I wonder what'll happen with the good luck between Yano and Nana, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I wonder if those two will get back together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If they really do break up, maybe I'll go out with Yano instead! Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still talking about that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizu-chin, why don't you get yourself a boyfriend already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Taka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't group us together. I... have one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear about that! Hey! I didn't hear a word about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear about that! I never heard you had a boyfriend, Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mizu-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a sec here! When was this? When? Where at? Who is it? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know all those episodes I haven't been in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I began to foster my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for me to be competing with Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was kinda having my own "Bokura ga Ita" all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is he older? Younger? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'll leave that to your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:52.56,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Imagination? What am I supposed to imagine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Mizoguchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:14:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo... atashi dake wo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:00.82,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Me too! I want to sing like that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a... a... "Mizu-chin was there too"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? All alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time we hold this special corner, I'll do it alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, please come and take me away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day before she died, we got into an argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was over something really stupid. Just a normal lover's quarrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's a day early, why don't we celebrate your birthday today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you remember that new pasta place that opened last month?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you eat as much as you want today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Actually, I just went there a couple days ago with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and Miki were bored one day, and these guys started hitting on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were college students.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we did was eat and talk, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you go with them so willingly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocchan, you haven't called me at all since summer break started, so I was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never called, and whenever I called your house, you were never there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I was working over at Take's, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't know about that. I don't remember hearing about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your little sister answered the phone, and I told her to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You told Yuri? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go eating food some other guy buys for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are stupid, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... what I said to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I guess I snapped, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she was always laughed about whatever I told her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at that time, she was seriously angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just like that, we went our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the accident happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no good when I have to remember her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there's so much I regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I become painfully aware of how powerless I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop asking myself questions, despite how futile they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ask yourself futile questions...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:17:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, you may not believe me, but right now, you're the most important person to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's because I believe only one person can be most important to you at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don't believe me, then there's nothing I can do, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The women I always want the most run away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The women I always want the most run away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I ever toss you away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my girlfriend was a cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop asking myself questions, despite how futile they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... everything I kept asking Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really think Nana-san loved you a whole lot, Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's regretting it even now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's really regretting leaving you behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She could just die for making you so sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure, even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she's watching over you from heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's heart was about to open up to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, this time... I won't make any mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Yano's heart will open all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-san didn't run from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just passed you by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really did love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she lost the chance to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never tossed you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... answer her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Nana-san's listening now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she wants to apologize to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer Nana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... why don't we both go searching for our own happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I couldn't make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:04.69,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuhi ga kage wo hosoku nobashita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:09.82,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro wo fukaku somete yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:16.66,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitto saigo no jikan da to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:23.34,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Namida koraeteta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:29.93,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Omoide nante itsumo kanashisugiru bakari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:36.72,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Isso wasurete shimaitai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:43.31,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nido to aenai kimi senaka to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:49.53,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Saigo no yuuhi mitsumetsudzuketa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.53,0:23:56.08,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsumo itsumo yasashisugita ne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:24:05.13,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima wa ososugiru keredo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.13,0:24:13.47,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the sunset kimi wo ushinaitakunai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.47,0:24:20.27,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora wo dakishimete tsutsumikomu you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.27,0:24:27.07,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Sotto utsumuita kimi no yokogao
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.07,0:24:37.74,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuhi yo kono mama shizumanaideite
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.74,0:24:44.88,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsumo sugoshita futari no heya to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.88,0:24:50.01,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,umi wo aruita photograph
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.01,0:25:03.52,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitotsu kawashita yakusoku ga hatasezu sugite yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.52,0:25:10.15,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokorobosoku natteta hitori no heya ni suwatte
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.15,0:25:16.74,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,tooku ni kikoeru amaoto
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.74,0:25:23.41,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuka wasurete iku kimochi naraba
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.41,0:25:29.71,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Konna ni kokoro kurushimenaide
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.71,0:25:34.88,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Sotto sotto kobore...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:04.69,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The sunset stretches my shadow long and thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:09.82,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Its colors deeply dye my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:16.66,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,When you said this was probably the last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:23.34,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I held back my tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:29.93,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories are always too sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:36.72,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to forget them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:43.31,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I continued to watch the last sunset
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:49.53,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and your back that I would never see again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.53,0:23:56.08,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,You were always too kind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:24:05.13,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and even though now's too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.13,0:24:13.47,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the sunset. I don't want to lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.47,0:24:20.27,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sky enveloping me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.27,0:24:27.07,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,your face would always look down at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.07,0:24:37.74,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it so the sun never sets...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.74,0:24:44.88,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The room we always lived in,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.88,0:24:50.01,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,that photograph when we walked on the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.01,0:25:03.52,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The promise we made will go unkept.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.52,0:25:10.15,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,I became so lonely alone in my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.15,0:25:16.74,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,listening to the distant rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.74,0:25:23.41,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,If these are just some feelings I'm going to forget one day
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.41,0:25:29.71,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,then don't torment my heart so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.71,0:25:34.88,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Gently, gently falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.91,0:25:34.93,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HDC6CE3&\c&HFDE2FF&\fscx97.5\fscy123.75\pos(430,377)}Episode 19 Preview ...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.61,0:25:08.15,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... you're\N pretty serious today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.15,0:25:10.15,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be because...\N I'm actually nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.15,0:25:12.90,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were\N going to tell me to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.90,0:25:16.37,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided that\N I want to start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.37,0:25:21.50,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... what's it mean to fight\N to the bitter end for love?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.50,0:25:25.46,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how we never notice\N the seasons changing...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.46,0:25:29.71,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...the same goes for our hearts.
